
---

## .gitignore (.NET 8 + Visual Studio/VS Code)

```gitignore
# ======================================
# .NET / Visual Studio / VS Code
# ======================================

# Build results
bin/
obj/
[Bb]uild/
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
x64/
x86/
[Aa]ny [Cc]PU/
[Ll]og/

# Test results / coverage
TestResults/
coveragereport/
*.trx
*.coverage
coverage.cobertura.xml
*.opencover.xml
*.lcov
*.log

# User-specific files
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.rsuser

# Visual Studio
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/

# Rider
*.sln.iml

# NuGet
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
.nuget/

# ASP.NET Scaffolding
ScaffoldingReadMe.txt

# Dotnet tools
.dotnet/
.tool/

# Environment files
.env
.env.*
appsettings.*.json
!appsettings.json

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# Logs
*.log

# Resharper
_ReSharper*/
*.[Rr]e[Ss]harper
*.DotSettings.user

# Packages (if any)
packages/

# Azure / publish
publish/
*.Publish.xml
*.pubxml
*.pubxml.user

# Docker (optional)
**/docker-compose.override.yml

# Node (if front-end exists)
node_modules/
dist/